# Cloudflare Turnstile CAPTCHA site key (public — pairs with the server's secret key).
# Get both free at https://dash.cloudflare.com -> Turnstile. Leave empty in dev:
# the captcha widget hides itself and the server skips verification.
# On Vercel, add this in Project Settings -> Environment Variables, then redeploy.
VITE_TURNSTILE_SITE_KEY=
